						<summary>

						<p>Highly damaged. Seems to record a gift of land for a flower garden by a member of the mint establishment <hi rend="italic">(Kambaṭṭattu Āṇikkāṟar)</hi> in the 7th regnal year of the king. The details of date viz., <hi rend="bold">7th year, Ṛishabha, ba. 5, Friday, Tiruvōṇam</hi> regularly correspond to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1261, May 20, ·62; ·55.</hi></p>						

